  "key_relationships": [
    "Composer extends PartialComposer (inheritance)",
    "Factory creates Composer via createComposer() — returns Composer|PartialComposer based on $fullLoad flag",
    "Factory creates PartialComposer via createComposer() when $fullLoad=false",
    "Factory::create() static shorthand → calls createComposer() with fullLoad=true",
    "Factory::createGlobal() static → calls createGlobalComposer() → calls createComposer()",
    "Installer::create(IOInterface, Composer) → static factory that reads Composer services and constructs Installer",
    "Installer depends_on Composer (constructor receives its services: DownloadManager, RepositoryManager, Locker, InstallationManager, EventDispatcher, AutoloadGenerator)",
    "Factory composes PartialComposer: sets Config, Loop, EventDispatcher, RepositoryManager, InstallationManager, Package",
    "Factory composes Composer (additional): sets DownloadManager, AutoloadGenerator, ArchiveManager, Locker, PluginManager",
    "Compiler is standalone build-time utility — uses ProcessExecutor, JsonFile, Finder, Phar; no runtime dependency on Composer class",
    "InstalledVersions is standalone runtime utility — uses ClassLoader for vendor discovery; no dependency on other Composer classes",
    "Compiler directly patches Composer.php source content (VERSION/BRANCH_ALIAS_VERSION/RELEASE_DATE constants) during phar build"
  ],

